title: Docusign Expands Its Developer Community With New Platform
author: Chris J Preimesberger
description: Digital signature provider unveils a suite of tools and resources for creating custom e-signature extensions at its inaugural Docusign Discover event.
cntitle: Docusign通过新平台扩展其开发者社区
cndescription: 数字签名提供商在其首届 Docusign Discover 活动上推出了一套用于创建自定义电子签名扩展的工具和资源。
